    <briefdescription>
<para>SD host controller I/O control structure. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Controls I/O settings for the SDHC. Note that only a subset of these settings apply to host controllers in SPI mode. Populate this struct, then call <ref refid="group__sdhc__interface_1ga0e6d8259cca442bd1356d00f668d35c4" kindref="member">sdhc_set_io</ref> to apply I/O settings </para>
